---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import InquiryForm from '../components/InquiryForm.astro';
import { aboutPageSchema } from '../lib/schema';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About WegoFulfill - Your China-Based Fulfillment Partner"
  description="Me— Five, the founder of WegoFulfill. A China sourcing and fulfillment partner built on technical precision, life-changing journeys, and the hard-earned lessons of global e-commerce."
  keywords="about WegoFulfill, China fulfillment company, Shenzhen fulfillment center, China sourcing agent, 3PL company China, ecommerce fulfillment partner"
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', url: '/' }, { name: 'About', url: '/about/' }]}
  schema={[aboutPageSchema()]}
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <!-- 1. Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-tag">Our Story</span>
      <h1>From Technology to <span>Supply Chain</span>.<br>Our Resilience, Your <span>Success</span>.</h1>
      <p>Me— Five, the founder of WegoFulfill. A story built on technical precision, life-changing journeys, and the hard-earned lessons of global e-commerce.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. About Hero (original kept) -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <div class="intro-text">
          <h2>About WegoFulfill</h2>
          <p class="lead">We are a China-based dropshipping agent and 3PL fulfillment partner located in Shenzhen, Guangdong Province &mdash; the heart of China's manufacturing and export hub.</p>
          <p>Our mission is simple: help overseas e-commerce sellers access Chinese supply chains directly, with transparent pricing and reliable fulfillment &mdash; no hidden fees, no monthly subscriptions, no minimum order quantities.</p>
          <p>Whether you sell on Shopify, WooCommerce, TikTok Shop, Amazon, eBay, or any other platform &mdash; we integrate seamlessly and handle the entire logistics chain from our Shenzhen warehouse.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-img">
          <img src="/images/five-family.jpg" alt="WegoFulfill Founder &amp; Family" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Story Rows -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Row 1: 2016 -->
      <div class="story-row">
        <div class="story-img">
          <img src="/images/five-family.jpg" alt="Five - Founder of WegoFulfill" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-text">
          <span class="story-badge">2016: The Beginning</span>
          <h2>Bridging Manufacturing &amp; Digital</h2>
          <p>Our founder is known simply as <strong>Five</strong>. In his family&mdash;a lineage where tradition and integrity are paramount&mdash;he is the 5th boy of his generation to be recorded in the family genealogy (族谱). This heritage instilled in him a lifelong commitment: to be as solid and reliable as his name suggests.</p>
          <p>Five&rsquo;s entrepreneurial spirit began in <strong>2016</strong>. While in college, he worked part-time building WordPress sites for local factories to fund his education. This was his first bridge between China&rsquo;s massive manufacturing power and the digital world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Row 2: 2018 Tibet (reversed) -->
      <div class="story-row story-row-reverse">
        <div class="story-img">
          <img src="/images/five-tibet.jpg" alt="Meeting Thalia in Tibet" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-text">
          <span class="story-badge">2018: Finding Clarity</span>
          <h2>A Journey to Tibet</h2>
          <p>After graduating in 201— Five secured a competitive IT role at a listed company. But he soon felt like a &ldquo;carrot in a pre-dug hole&rdquo;&mdash;restricted by corporate walls and losing sight of his original passion.</p>
          <p>In August 201— Five walked away from his stable IT job to find his &ldquo;初心&rdquo; (original intention). He traveled to the pure, high-altitude landscapes of Tibet. Amidst the silence of the mountains, he found clarity and met <strong>Thalia</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Row 3: 2019-2020 -->
      <div class="story-row">
        <div class="story-img">
          <img src="/images/five-chair.png" alt="Five building a chair brand" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-text">
          <span class="story-badge">2019–2020: New Beginnings</span>
          <h2>Shenzhen, Marriage &amp; E-Commerce</h2>
          <p>Thalia was a dental nurse in Shenzhen, a profession requiring surgical precision and deep care. In 201— Five moved to Shenzhen to be with her, joined an advertising agency, and discovered the world of Dropshipping through YouTube. He spent his nights self-studying, combining his IT background with his new-found passion for e-commerce.</p>
          <p>In 202— Five opened an AliExpress store and realized the massive demand for reliable China agents. That year, he married Thalia and welcomed their son. To support his family, he joined a high-growth cross-border venture, building a brand for office and gaming chairs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Row 4: 2021-2023 (reversed) -->
      <div class="story-row story-row-reverse">
        <div class="story-img">
          <img src="/images/wegofulfill-team.jpg" alt="WegoFulfill Team" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-text">
          <span class="story-badge">2021–2023: The Peak &amp; The Pitfall</span>
          <h2>Lessons from the Heights</h2>
          <p>The pandemic brought explosive growth. The company scaled to 100+ employees in record time. However, success masked a fatal flaw: <strong>supply chain and inventory management</strong>. In 2023, the weight of unsold stock and logistics bottlenecks led to the company&rsquo;s closure.</p>
          <p>F— Five, 2023 wasn&rsquo;t just a failure; it was a <strong>Masterclass in Supply Chain</strong>. He saw firsthand the disasters that can destroy a brand. He gained a perspective on the world that most agents will never have.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Row 5: 2024 -->
      <div class="story-row">
        <div class="story-img">
          <img src="/images/wegofulfill-team.jpg" alt="WegoFulfill Rebirth - Branded Dropshipping" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-text">
          <span class="story-badge">2024: A Fresh Start</span>
          <h2>The Shift to Branded Dropshipping</h2>
          <p>In 202— Five started again from zero. He reconnected with his old dropshipping friends and saw a new trend: <strong>The shift towards Branded Dropshipping.</strong> Sellers were no longer just moving generic products&mdash;they were building real brands with custom packaging, logos, and customer loyalty. And they needed a fulfillment partner who understood that.</p>
          <p>WegoFulfill was reborn&mdash;with a sharper focus, deeper supply chain knowledge, and a personal understanding of what it takes to succeed in global e-commerce.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Timeline Strip -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="timeline-strip">
        <div class="time-item"><strong>2016</strong><span>WP Dev for<br>Factories</span></div>
        <div class="time-item"><strong>2017</strong><span>Listed Co.<br>IT Specialist</span></div>
        <div class="time-item"><strong>2018</strong><span>The Tibet<br>Revelation</span></div>
        <div class="time-item"><strong>2019</strong><span>Shenzhen<br>Ad Agency</span></div>
        <div class="time-item"><strong>2020</strong><span>AliExpress &amp;<br>Marriage</span></div>
        <div class="time-item"><strong>2021–23</strong><span>High-Scale<br>Brand Exp.</span></div>
        <div class="time-item"><strong>2024</strong><span>WegoFulfill<br>Rebirth</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. What This Means for You -->
  <section class="section values-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="value-dark-item">
          <h3>&#128300; Surgical QC</h3>
          <p>Guided by Thalia&rsquo;s background, our QC process isn&rsquo;t just a check; it&rsquo;s a rigorous inspection to protect your brand&rsquo;s reputation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-dark-item">
          <h3>&#128187; IT-Driven Automation</h3>
          <p>Five&rsquo;s IT roots mean we prioritize automation and seamless store integrations (Shopify, TikTok Shop, etc.).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-dark-item">
          <h3>&#128200; Inventory Wisdom</h3>
          <p>Having seen companies fail due to inventory, we help you manage stock and scaling risks effectively.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. What Sets Us Apart -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
        <p>Not another middleman &mdash; we are your on-the-ground team in China</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#127970;</div>
          <h3>Based in Shenzhen</h3>
          <p>Direct access to factories, suppliers, and logistics networks in the world's electronics and manufacturing capital. No middlemen, no markups.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#128176;</div>
          <h3>No Monthly Fees</h3>
          <p>We don't charge subscription or monthly fees. You only pay per order &mdash; product cost + fulfillment handling + shipping. Fully transparent pricing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#128241;</div>
          <h3>Priority Support</h3>
          <p>Direct WhatsApp communication with your dedicated agent. Fast response times, real-time updates, and a team that knows your business personally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#128200;</div>
          <h3>Scale With You</h3>
          <p>From 5 orders/day to 1,000+. Our infrastructure and team scale seamlessly as your business grows &mdash; no disruption, no growing pains.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#127760;</div>
          <h3>Global Reach</h3>
          <p>Ship to 200+ countries via YunExpress, 4PX, DHL, FedEx, and other major carriers. Reliable tracking and DDP options available.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">&#127919;</div>
          <h3>No MOQ</h3>
          <p>Start with as few orders as you need. We negotiate MOQs with suppliers on your behalf so you can test products risk-free and scale at your own pace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 7. Signature -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center; max-width:700px;">
      <blockquote class="signature-quote">
        <p>&ldquo;Whether you are shipping your first order or scaling to thousands, we treat your business as our own. We&rsquo;ve seen the highs and the lows, and we are here to ensure your journey is smooth, transparent, and built for the long haul.&rdquo;</p>
        <span class="signature-name">— Five</span>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 8. Our Warehouse -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="warehouse-section">
        <div class="warehouse-content">
          <h2>Our Warehouse</h2>
          <p>Our fulfillment center is located in Longhua District, Shenzhen &mdash; minutes away from major logistics hubs. The facility features:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Climate-controlled storage for sensitive products</li>
            <li>CCTV monitoring and secure access control</li>
            <li>Dedicated picking and packing zones</li>
            <li>Real-time inventory management system</li>
            <li>90 days free storage for all clients</li>
            <li>Custom packaging and kitting stations</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Our warehouse team processes orders daily with a 99.9% accuracy rate. Every item goes through systematic pick-pack-verify before dispatch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="warehouse-img">
          <div class="img-placeholder">Shenzhen Warehouse</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 9. Stats -->
  <section class="section stats-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-block"><strong>1,000+</strong><span>Daily Order Capacity</span></div>
        <div class="stat-block"><strong>200+</strong><span>Countries Served</span></div>
        <div class="stat-block"><strong>99.9%</strong><span>Order Accuracy</span></div>
        <div class="stat-block"><strong>24h</strong><span>Processing Time</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <InquiryForm
    title="Want to Work With Us?"
    subtitle="Send us your product details and we'll provide a free, no-obligation quote."
  />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Hero ===== */
  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, var(--color-bg-alt) 0%, var(--color-bg) 70%);
    border-radius: 0 0 40px 40px;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #dbeafe;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-hero h1 { font-size: 3.25rem; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .about-hero h1 span { color: var(--color-primary); }
  .about-hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-light); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

  /* ===== About Intro ===== */
  .about-intro { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .intro-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .intro-text .lead { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .intro-text p { color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .intro-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }

  /* ===== Story Rows ===== */
  .story-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 5rem; }
  .story-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .story-row-reverse { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; }
  .story-row-reverse .story-img { order: 2; }
  .story-row-reverse .story-text { order: 1; }
  .story-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .story-img-placeholder {
    width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-primary-light));
    border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #fff; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .story-img-placeholder.dark { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg-dark), #4a5568); }
  .story-badge {
    display: inline-block; background: #dbeafe; color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .story-text h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .story-text p { color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .story-text p strong { color: var(--color-primary-dark); }

  /* ===== Timeline ===== */
  .timeline-strip { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
  .time-item { padding: 20px 10px; background: var(--color-bg); border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
  .time-item strong { display: block; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .time-item span { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--color-text-light); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; }

  /* ===== Values Dark ===== */
  .values-dark { background: var(--color-bg-dark); color: #fff; border-radius: 24px; text-align: center; }
  .values-dark h2 { color: #fff; font-size: 2.25rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .value-dark-item h3 { color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .value-dark-item p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ===== Value Cards ===== */
  .value-card { background: var(--color-bg); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); text-align: center; transition: all var(--transition); }
  .value-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
  .value-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .value-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .value-card p { color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* ===== Signature ===== */
  .signature-quote p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.9; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .signature-name { font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary); }

  /* ===== Warehouse ===== */
  .warehouse-section { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .warehouse-content h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .warehouse-content p { color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .warehouse-content ul { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .warehouse-content li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text); }
  .img-placeholder {
    width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-primary-light));
    border-radius: var(--radius); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #fff; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* ===== Stats ===== */
  .stats-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-dark), var(--color-primary)); color: #fff; }
  .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .stat-block strong { display: block; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .stat-block span { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; }
    .about-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .story-row, .story-row-reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .story-row-reverse .story-img { order: -1; }
    .story-row-reverse .story-text { order: 0; }
    .story-text h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .timeline-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
    .warehouse-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .values-dark { border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .timeline-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
